  "detailed_description": "If you like Match 3 games, you need this game in your collection!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse your mouse to swipe through the fruits and collect them all.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game contains 100 levels with exciting achievements.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nComplete all mission types:<br />\r\n- Reach the target score<br />\r\n- Gather specific fruits<br />\r\n- Remove colored tiles<br />\r\n- Collect trophies<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game has 2 challenging variations:<br />\r\n- Time limits<br />\r\n- Move limits<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCan you complete all 100 levels?",
